Output terminal/rendered/05-qubo-smoke.mp4
Output terminal/rendered/05-qubo-smoke.gif
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1280
Set Height 720
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 25ms
Set Padding 20

Type "# QUBO bridge smoke (no Datadog / LLM)"
Enter
Sleep 300ms
Type "# From repo root:"
Enter
Type "./scripts/qubo-e2e-smoke.sh"
Enter
Sleep 400ms
Type "# Optional: --verbose  --log=/tmp/smoke.log  --skip-mvn"
Enter
Type "# Sets PYTHON to dice-leap-poc/.venv, runs toy solve + JVM IT"
Enter
Sleep 2s
